{
  "stem": "21788.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then of course what happened was, ah-ha, now that you're leaving, you have to leave your wealth, or most of your wealth, behind.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Matter of fact, you had to turn in your gold, your silver, your diamonds.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, my father, I think, was struggling in those years, from 1925 till his business was closed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He-- well, he wasn't a millionaire, but he wasn't poor, either.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would say just upper middle class.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I would say upper middle class.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then, after he closed-- after the business was closed, ironically speaking, he was making more money than he ever did before because now he was working illegally.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And what he mostly did was, he took and made dentures out of gold, pure gold, especially lower dentures, because the Jews could not take their jewelry out.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they melted the gold, and they made the dentures, especially the lower dentures, out of gold.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, that's very obvious, right, but in those days dentures were made, not of-- not out of plastic, but they were made out of vulcanite, rubber.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he made the denture out of gold and covered it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The teeth were on top, and covered it, all around with vulcanite, and also the bottom, so the gold was hidden inside the denture.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I'm saying this, especially with lower dentures, because you can make them quite big.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The upper ones would fall down, but the lower ones would stay in place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This was not something that you would eat with, this was just something you stuck in your mouth when you get across the border.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Well, there was always quite a bit of waste gold, and my father, first of all, charged, of course, for that, and there was always something left over for him.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
